3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the generation of photo-realistic images using a novel approach. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image generation and manipulation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the generation of images using a cross-modal approach involving both keypoint and image data.
